# Direct dependencies for the CI test-spark job.
#
# Regenerate the committed hashed lockfile with:
#   PROFILES=spark VERSIONS=3.14 ./bin/generate-lockfiles.sh
#
# Pin rationale:
# - Core Graphistry runtime deps: lets CI install graphistry with --no-deps
#   while keeping the full smoke-test environment hashed.
# - pyspark: Spark runtime exercised by graphistry/tests/compute/* spark tests.
# - pyarrow/pandas: Spark<->DataFrame interchange surfaces used by those tests.
# - requests: direct PyGraphistry runtime dependency included by the prior smoke env.
# - pytest: test runner for the focused spark lane.
